params.name: data.stats

These can be requested by setting [ExecuteSqlRequest.query_mode][google.spanner.v1.ExecuteSqlRequest.query_mode]. DML statements always produce stats containing the number of rows modified, unless executed using the [ExecuteSqlRequest.QueryMode.PLAN][google.spanner.v1.ExecuteSqlRequest.QueryMode.PLAN] [ExecuteSqlRequest.query_mode][google.spanner.v1.ExecuteSqlRequest.query_mode]. Other fields may or may not be populated, based on the [ExecuteSqlRequest.query_mode][google.spanner.v1.ExecuteSqlRequest.query_mode].
